title: Looking for D5+ Jungler (German / Swiss / Austrian) - March Marmots
body:
Hello everyone, I am Michi "MilchikeksCH" the vice president of March Marmots and we are looking for a german speaking Jungler.

Preferably in the D5 area or higher.
German / Swiss / Austrian
Training around 2-3 times a week towards the evening around 19:00 - 23:00 (Days TBD)
Able to join us at offline events if possible and we would play in SESL and ESL.
Help us build this org up!
Interested? Message our team captain Max "Maxiethunder", League IGN: MM Maxiethunder

http://euw.op.gg/multi/query=mmfinn%2Cm%CF%82cree%2Cmmmaxiethunder%2Cmmbiatsch
